### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8081/api/auth/health

### Register New User
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "researcher@labverse.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "fullName": "John Doe",
  "username": "johndoe",
  "roleName": "RESEARCHER"
}

### Login with Email and Password
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "researcher@labverse.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Google OAuth2 Login
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/google
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idToken": "YOUR_GOOGLE_ID_TOKEN_HERE"
}

### Get Current User (Replace YOUR_JWT_TOKEN with actual token from login/register response)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Register PI (Principal Investigator)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "pi@labverse.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "fullName": "Dr. Jane Smith",
  "username": "janesmith",
  "roleName": "PI"
}

### Register Student
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student@labverse.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "fullName": "Alice Johnson",
  "username": "alicejohnson",
  "roleName": "STUDENT"
}

### Forgot Password
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "researcher@labverse.com"
}

### Logout
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

### ===== PROFILE MANAGEMENT =====

### Get Current User Profile (Need JWT Token)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Update Profile
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "johndoe_updated",
  "fullName": "John Doe Updated",
  "avatarUrl": "https://example.com/avatar.jpg"
}

### Change Password
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/users/me/password
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "password123",
  "newPassword": "newpassword123"
}

### Delete Account (Soft Delete)
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get User by ID
GET http://localhost:8081/api/users/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

